
You will probably need to install libX11-devel package for this to compile

yum install libX11-devel

Run the MPI parallel program to calculate PI using Monte Carlo method

pbsget -4
mpiexec -n 4 monte <epsilon>
exit

Run the MPI parallel program that shows an animation to calculate PI using Monte Carlo method

pbsget -4
mpiexec -n 4 monte-anim <epsilon>
exit
